verbose_text: In accordance with the level of mHOIP, cpdm MEFs expressing mSHARPIN LTM mut, but not WT, could not prevent caspase mediated cell death following stimulation with TNF-alpha plus cycloheximide (CHX) or effectively induce degradation of IkappaBa, a hallmark of NF-kappaB activation, in response to TNF-alpha (XREF_FIG).
